title: Am I a Vegan Psychopath? (Politics & Personal Consequences)
description: The controversy-of-the-moment (that created this video) was a guy called Joe Best leaning heavily on allegations that I'm a psychopath, but, as always, I try to talk about broader (and more meaningful) issues in a way that would make this video interesting if I came back and watched it myself a few years from now.
